metadata.name: META//MEME: 69 Books of Genesis #1/69
metadata.description:
META//MEME is a living art collection, visualizes our history & the meta-shifts that have defined us. Expressed through our chosen form; memes mold our language and the digital persona behind them. 

META//ONE//RAREPEPE. The RarePepes were our first community meta. A beautiful mesh of dank humor, crypto degens & community//creators. 69 Books of Genesis honors the 'moment of inspiration, the memetic stars aligning, the canvas of the craven perfected'

This card grants the holder special powers and privileges ;)
